author: Dominik Kalaminec
title: Dominik Kalaminec
text: I was a real pleasure working with Nengun Performance. I inquired about a part that wasn't listed on their website. They responded to my question very promptly, and not only were they able to obtain the part I was looking for they added it to their site for future customer to be able to purchase. Absolutely flawless service, great communication (there was slight delay in availability -which they communicated right away), and fast shipping. Over a great experience. I will definitely be shopping from Nengun Performance again!
